Insider Activity


Individual




Tanya Styblo Beder



Ms. Tanya S. Beder is Independent Director at CYS Investments, Inc. and Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at SBCC Group, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at CYS Investments, Inc., OpHedge Investment Services LLC, American Century Investments Value Yield LLC, and Institute For Pure & Applied Mathematics.
Ms. Beder was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer by Tribeca Global Management LLC, Chairman by International Association of Financial Engineers, a Manager by Citigroup, Inc., and a Managing Director by Caxton Associates LP.
She received her undergraduate degree from Yale University and an MBA from Harvard University.



