Financial Engineering: The Evolution of a Profession




                        By 
                                
Tanya S. Beder

                             and 
                                
Tanya S. S. Beder

                             and 
                                
Cara M. Marshall

                             and 
                                
Cara M. M. Marshall





Business & Economics : Finance





                            Wiley
                            Publication date: May 2011



                            ISBN: 9780470889817
                        



                    Digital Book format: PDF (Adobe DRM)
                




